\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"362f9c7bc3787dfe24473d6ac011c672fd8b8ede","tid":1662194,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a59545f1781f34696cf2cd7169e2e48cab99369","tid":1662194,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"233714cfec81f9fb61e67e018b694598d5a4ab76","tid":1662194,"uid":179990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"男人三十而立<br />\n加上事業開始起步<br />\n望到啲18,22嘅 <br />\n再諗下屋企個個已經30歲<br />\n真係好大考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cebf4c09ba97accb9cda24f2a33a315cee2ae8","tid":1662194,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"I don't see why there's a problem with it. My friend Joe is 26 whereas his girlfriend is 33 and their parents are very supportive of them. Joe isn't very well-to-do while his girlfriend's family is very well-off. Yesterday he threw a party at his place in which cheap wine was served. The sofas in his flat are made of some cheap material. His television is cheap and nasty. Recently he got lots of clothes on the cheap as the shop is about to go into liquidation. He bought a pair of cheap shoes that fell apart after a couple months so I bought him some good quality shoes. He's too mean to buy new shoes. He's very cheap with the air conditioner too- it's only on for an hour each day then he turns on the fans and opens the windows instead. He holidayed in macau last week but has so cheap he didn't even buy is postcards. He stayed at a four star hotel that serves cheap and cheerful food and sells cheap and cheerful clothes. He's a pianist. He said &quot;this passage should be played beautifully rather than rhythmically. Otherwise it's a bit cheap.&quot; He asked me to get some Haydn scores for him as I can get them on the cheap from a friend of mine. We watched a kickboxing fight in which Paul hit Josh with a cheap shot after he lost to josh. We watched john vs anthony as well. The referee could've stopped the match which would've been a cheap triumph for anthony but fortunately he didn't. We also watched a comedy show which was full of cheap laughs. The comedian is famous for his vulgar manner. His jokes and jibes were cheap and vulgar. Today dogs and cats certainly don't come cheap. Ken bought a massage chair for my birthday. Massage chairs like this don't come cheap. Ken is invited to a marathon next week but he may be out of condition for it."},{"pid":"3c296b0cf549fec364a289ceeac45d9ec46613c9","tid":1662194,"uid":300013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔得？大把人啦 ching"},{"pid":"b2a4bcfda97d5b31a64c113682b3d7d7be4f30b2","tid":1662194,"uid":75726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"無問題<br />\n有朋友34女 27男<br />\n下年結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地18男 25女 一齊過<br />\n之後有散過 但前幾年又一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係愛呀"},{"pid":"12805c182ee47c4a3da4fc5f5d63c3a3b09e4107","tid":1662194,"uid":95134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"壓力都黎自屋企人，2老都極力反對"},{"pid":"c58fca83255bc3071e536af3e3708c3d1da86b4c","tid":1662194,"uid":119767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"我27個時試過37<br />\n不過最後我接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b191ea62a60868afb317bc2205688c4a7074164","tid":1662194,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit